VAR_GLOBAL gDiagState : lib500_types.DIAG_STATUS; // ECU diagnostic status
gPowerStage : t_Power; // Powerstage status structure gSafetySwitch0 : t_Power; // Safety Switch 0 status structure gSensorSupply : t_Power; // Sensor Supply status structure gPotRed : lib500_types.IO_ADC_STATUS; // Red Potentiometer value gLedRed : t_PWM; // Led Red output gCan1 : tCan; // Structure for sending / receiving CAN messages END_VAR
{attribute 'qualified_only'} VAR_GLOBAL CONSTANT MAJOR : BYTE := 1; // SW Version major MINOR : BYTE := 0; // SW Version minor PATCH : BYTE := 8; // SW Version patch END_VAR

TYPE t_Power : STRUCT // structure for POWER outputs Set : lib500_types.IO_POWER_STATUS := (state := lib500_types.IO_POWER_STATE.IO_POWER_OFF); // set power output state Get : lib500_types.IO_POWER_STATUS := (state := lib500_types.IO_POWER_STATE.IO_POWER_OFF); // get power output state Feedback : lib500_types.IO_ADC_STATUS; // get power output voltage feetback END_STRUCT END_TYPE

TYPE t_PWM : STRUCT // structure for PWM outputs DutyCycle : WORD := 0; // pin duty cycle Error : lib500_types.IO_ERRORTYPE; // pin errorcode CurrMeasurement : lib500_types.IO_PWM_CURRENT_QUEUE_E; // pin current measurement CurrentValue : WORD; // usable current value PWMFeedback : lib500_types.IO_PWM_FEEDBACK; // voltage feedback END_STRUCT END_TYPE
